QUESTION NO: 1
ECM is the technology that brings unstructured information together and organizes it in a
structured way. Which of the following is not an example of unstructured data?
A. ERP Application
B. Financial Report
C. HR Email with Policy Attachments
D. Hardcopy load application
Answer: A
